Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NWah! Wa― Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess who's here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm on your side, all right?\NNo matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Au... Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Ah-eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right, bud.\NIt's me, Kage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE grunts]\NDon't cry, Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be big boys, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAh. Au, au. [sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, if you could\Nsee your face right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ah, eh, ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what, bud?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been with you\Nevery last step of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] When you fell off the\Ntower and bonked your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] When that thief\Nran off with your bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] When you were about to\Nbite into that poisoned meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right there\Nto help you out each time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as I hate to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,your life is still in\Na lot of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Back at the castle, that snake\Nguy asked me to escort you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHe's tough to read, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure what he's really up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, until we\Ncould figure out who was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,coming after you, we had to keep\Nall this a secret from you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta fool your friends\Nto fool your foes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way life\Ncan be sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the way we came―\NWe're heading deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be talking to\Nsomeone who can make you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the mightiest man there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, he's way down\Nthere in the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NEnter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NYou called, Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Domas. When you\Nvoted for the next king,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,why did you throw in\Nyour lot with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS gasps]\NHow could you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The weight of the crown is more\Nthan Prince Bojji could bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Also... if I might be so bold,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you measure up better\Nto be the king―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You believed I would be\Na better fit for the throne?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- [snarls]\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And did you think nothing\Nof your duty to your pupil,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you coward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You betrayed my brother\Nin handing me the crown
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and brought disgrace\Nupon my court!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NI've no defense, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA] Tch. On that day,\Nafter I sparred with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure you were\Nsomeone I could trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you've defied\Nmy best expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NDomas...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You are an extraordinarily\Ncapable man,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and I long dreamed you\Nwould serve as my right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in leading this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that will stay a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not who\NI thought you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NKing Daida, how can I fix this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA] For the sake of\Nthis kingdom and its people,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come to a decision,\Nbut what must be done next
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is something I could\Nonly ask of a servant
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,whom I can trust absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NPlease! You can trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NI should be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done my duty\Nto king and country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This pain in my heart must be\Npunishment for the weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of my resolve.\NSurely, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing else\Nit could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NThis is a deep hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still not to the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NIt's just a little cloth crown,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'll look way\Nmore like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Au-ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- [BOJJI] Hmph!\N- Yeah! There's the real Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your whole get-up feels a little\Ngeneric without it, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NHmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NEgad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NA human skull...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck could've\Nhappened down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniffing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAu, ah, au.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You smell something? Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI sniffing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out, gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where those pillars\Nof fire come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[horse shoes clopping]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA] I never realized\Nhow deep this passage went.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirror. What are you, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] A sworn ally\Nwho shared the joys and sorrows
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:08:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A satisfactory answer, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NHmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...\N[gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NThey are both loyal servants
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of the late King Bosse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And they shall aid you\Nin assuming his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NPlease, enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:09:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] Here,\Nyou will find many creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,all entombed in ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NWhat is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NFather!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] He was\Nbrought here after his death,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to be preserved,\Nin preparation for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[metal creaking]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what's happening, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[gears grinding]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[grinding continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA retches]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You monsters!\NHow could you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] This is where\Nit begins, King Daida.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[GRIFFIN 5A screeches]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] In that ball,\Nthe marrow of King Bosse's bones
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is being mixed with a secret\Npotion that I provided.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this madness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] The lenses are\Nfocusing the light on the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,heating it and\Nchanging its contents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NIt's glowing like the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NIt hatches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[PHOENIX 5A roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA grunts]\NThis is disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[PHOENIX 5A screeches]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[PHOENIX 5A roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[PHOENIX 5A screeches]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NIts blood is holy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] Its body has\Nbeen burned, and from its ashes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the Jewel of Resurrection\Ncan now be retrieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] This ingredient\Nwill complete the elixir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NNow. Drink, King Daida.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You would have me drink this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] Once you do,\Nyou will gain the almighty power
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of King Bosse.\NA power unrivaled in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NNow, drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I trust\Nthis vile concoction?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NBut King Daida, does that mean
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do what you're asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NHave you forgotten your drop
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in the ranking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I forget?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly the reason\NI have to try harder,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,for as long as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] Venturing into\Nthis world, you'll find that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it refuses to slow its workings\Nto accommodate your pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NI realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so...\NI don't know why,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I just can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] Indeed,\Nyour hesitation is only natural,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but what you stand to\Ngain by drinking that elixir
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is power beyond imagining.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you should\Ndrink it yourself, Mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what about the two\Nof you?! Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] It will have no\Neffect unless drunk by one
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,bearing the blood of King Bosse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do please try and\Nimagine it, King Daida.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Assuming the power of\NKing Bosse as your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and using it to soar\Nthrough the Ranking of Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine reigning\Nover all the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NAnd if I drink this, will I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Daida, no endeavor\Nworth your while
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,will offer an easy path.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,At times, your struggles\Nwill define you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep that in mind, and don't be\Ndeceived by those around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or especially yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NI won't drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NKing Daida―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NThen so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NIt is for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NDo not trifle with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NMirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be true that you're\Nacting in my interest,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but no. I will take\Nthe top rank by my own power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NStop. Y-You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Master Domas!\NThere you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO] Um. Wait.\NBut where is Prince Bojji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji is\Nno longer with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Has he gone somewhere, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Domas? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not in this world anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NGuh― You can't mean he―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[fire booming]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NAh... Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it isn't so...\NSurely, you could never...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESHA] Hmm. Then they\Nsurvived the cursed gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESHA]\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They each came bearing\Na curse already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, the gas\Nwouldn't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One is a giant\Nstripped of his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The other, a shadow clan\Nmember in an altered form,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,marked by divine disfavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:19:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Though indeed, the little crown\Nis undoubtedly the work
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of a master craftsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]\NYou've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This will suitably pass my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN 5A]\NSire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESHA]\NHeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah!\N- [KAGE] Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESHA] Hmph. I see.\NThe son of Bosse has come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NMaster Domas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The goal of this excursion\Nwas to eliminate Prince Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you were willing to\Naccept that mission...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he really dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- [DOMAS] Yes.\N- [growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NBy my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NYou dare...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've failed my duty\Nto protect Prince Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:19:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NQuit while you can!
