Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I been doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[snarls]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[huffing]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[splortch]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now follow that strike\Nthrough and sever my hand!
